      {
        "comment": "prefer-tag-over-role on interactive/custom widgets or wrong semantic suggestions (rich-editor div, drag-handle separators, custom listbox option, nested-interactive rows) — verified false positives. Paths listed both project-relative and root-relative to match either scan invocation.",
        "files": [
          "src/components/InlineEditor.tsx",
